title: #90: Proof Of UFOs With Shaan Joshi
description: Welcome to another exciting episode of Tin Foil Hat With Sam Tripoli. This episode Sam and Ryan welcome from "The Fanatics" podcast, Shaan Joshi, to break down the actual data on UFOs. Please check out Shaan's new podcast "The Fanatics" that's available on iTunes.  Thank you for your passion and we appreciate your support.
